# TMA Child Script

############################
# TEST STEP: Configure TDD #
############################

#-----------------------
# Set TDD Configuration
#-----------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Subframe Assignment
# 2. Special Subframe Patterns
#-----------------------
#                     1 2
#                     | |
forw mte PhySetTDDCfg 1 7
#-----------------------

######################################
# TEST STEP: Configure Uplink Timing #
######################################

#----------------------------------------------
# Configure uplink timing adjustment operation
#----------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. UL timing operation
# 2. UE Id
#----------------------------------------------
#                          1 2 
#                          | | 
forw mte PhyConfigUlTiming 6(0)
#----------------------------------------------

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
setp RRC_TEST_IGNORE_IRLC_ERROR_IND 1
#--

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
FORW L1 Msg4BypassContentionResolution 1
#--

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
SETP RRC_TEST_ENABLE_UL_TIME_ALIGN_TIMER 0
#--

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
SETP RRC_TEST_DISABLE_MAX_SR_TRANSMISSIONS 1
#--

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
SETP RRC_PUCCH_CLOSE_LOOP_POWER_CONTROL 0
#--

###############################
# TEST STEP: Raw Text Command #
###############################

#--
SETP RRC_NUM_DL_ANTENNAS 2
#--

# Set the uplink power offsets for multiple UEs
#-----------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Number of UEs
# 2. UE Context Id
# 3. PUCCH Power Offset
# 4. PRACH Power Offset
# 5. PUSCH Power Offset
# 6. SRS Power Offset

# Configure an EPS bearer data entity
#-------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data entity Id
# 2. EPS bearer Id
#-------------------------------------
#                          1 2
#                          | |
forw mte DeConfigEpsBearer 1 5
#-------------------------------------

#----------------------------------------------------------------
# Configure a pseudo noise evaluator attribute for a data entity
#----------------------------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data Entity Id
# 2. Sequence Type
#----------------------------------------------------------------
#                          1 2
#                          | |
forw mte DeConfigPneAttrib 1 2
#----------------------------------------------------------------

# Configure a UDP/IP port attribute for a data entity

# 3. Destination UDP port number
# 4. Source UDP port number
# 5. Maximum source UDP packet size
#-----------------------------------------------------
#                          1 2       3 4    5   
#                          | |       | |    |   
forw mte DeConfigUdiAttrib 1 0.0.0.0 0 5410 1000
#-----------------------------------------------------

# Configure a UDP/IP port attribute for a data entity
#-----------------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data Entity Id
# 2. Destination IP address
# 3. Destination UDP port number
# 4. Source UDP port number
# 5. Maximum source UDP packet size
#-----------------------------------------------------
#                          1 2       3 4    5   
#                          | |       | |    |   
forw mte DeConfigUdiAttrib 1 0.0.0.0 0 5559 1000
#-----------------------------------------------------

#----------------------------
# Set the current UE context
#----------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. UE context Id
#----------------------------
#                     1  
#                     |  
forw mte SetUEContext 150

# Configure an EPS bearer data entity
#-------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data entity Id
# 2. EPS bearer Id
#-------------------------------------
#                          1 2
#                          | |
forw mte DeConfigEpsBearer 1 5
#-------------------------------------

#----------------------------------------------------------------
# Configure a pseudo noise evaluator attribute for a data entity
#----------------------------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data Entity Id
# 2. Sequence Type
#----------------------------------------------------------------
#                          1 2
#                          | |
forw mte DeConfigPneAttrib 1 2
#----------------------------------------------------------------

#-----------------------------------------------------
# Configure a UDP/IP port attribute for a data entity
#-----------------------------------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. Data Entity Id
# 2. Destination IP address
# 3. Destination UDP port number
# 4. Source UDP port number
# 5. Maximum source UDP packet size
#-----------------------------------------------------
#                          1 2       3 4    5   
#                          | |       | |    |   
forw mte DeConfigUdiAttrib 1 0.0.0.0 0 5605 1000
#-----------------------------------------------------

#----------------------------
# Set the current UE context
#----------------------------
# PARAMETERS
# 1. UE context Id
#----------------------------
#                     1  
#                     |  
forw mte SetUEContext 196
#----------------------------
